The feature of namespacing and control groups is specific to linux OS not to Windows/MacOS.
When docker for MacOS/Windows gets installed, it installs Linux Virtual Machine under the hood.
When docker is running, it actually runs the Linux VM inside. Inside this VM where all the
containers get created. 


